&lt;li&gt;Experience analyzing VLAN, routing, IP addressing and sub-netting.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with Palo Alto firewalls, F5 appliances, and Splunk systems.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience troubleshooting and configuring IP networks using at least one of the following routing methods: BGP, ISIS OSPF, or Static routing.&lt;/li&gt;
