&lt;p&gt;C3EL is seeking a cleared &lt;strong&gt;Senior Project Manager &amp;amp; Site Lead&lt;/strong&gt; to join our on-site team at Fort Shafter Flats in Honolulu, Hawaii. This position serves as the primary on-site leader responsible for overall contract execution, mission continuity, and the daily direction of enterprise IT operations. The Senior Project Manager will oversee technical and administrative functions supporting a Network Operations and Security Center, ensuring optimal performance, compliance, and coordination across the program.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responsibilities will include, but not be limited to:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
