&lt;li&gt;Manage staffing, workload prioritization, task assignment, and performance tracking for all contract personnel.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Act as the primary point of contact and liaison with government stakeholders, including the Contracting Officer’s Representative (COR).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Oversee all DIACAP and Risk Management Framework (RMF) certification activities and ensure program deliverables meet compliance and quality standards.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Direct enterprise network and cybersecurity operations, ensuring consistent adherence to established SLAs and DoD policies.&lt;/li&gt;
